NO NFO 
Crack type: Patched .dll or patched .exe
Windows only
                                               
                ____________________________________________________



[Installation] 

1. Extract and run CCMaker.
2. Download and install whatever product you want. (Be sure to select the same exact version of CC 2019 programs listed above, the cracks are only valid for this version, prior versions won't work and future versions may need a new crack if adobe patches something)
3. When installation is done replace the provided cracked .dll or .exe in the installation directory of the aformentioned product.
4. Logout from Creative Cloud and block all of the installed products with a firewall and do not update them.
5. Enjoy !
